[0.056056, "o", "\r\nInstructions (2):\r\n  my-new-inst: My New Inst\r\n  tui-manual-test: TUI Manual Testing — Test TUI changes against a throwaway project in the workdir\r\n\r\nRegression Tests (21):\r\n  command-dedup: Command Deduplication — Test that PR actions block concurrent/duplicate execution\r\n  guide-progress: Guide Progress Widget — Test that guide progress widget displays correct step indicators\r\n  help-keybindings: Help Screen & Keybindings — Open help screen with ? and verify all documented keybindings work\r\n  init-empty: Init: Empty Repo — Test pm init with an empty repo (no commits) -- verifies backend, commands, TUI\r\n  init-github: Init: GitHub Repo — Test pm init with a GitHub remote -- verifies backend, commands, TUI\r\n  init-local: Init: Local Repo — Test pm init with a local repo (no remote) -- verifies backend, commands, TUI\r\n  launch-dedup: Pane Launch Deduplication — Test that pane launch keys (g, n) don't create duplicates\r\n  log-viewer: TUI Log Viewer — Test L key opens log pane, verify content"]
[0.056177, "o", " and pane lifecycle\r\n  meta-launch: Meta Session Launch — Test m key launches meta pane with correct role and context\r\n  mobile-mode: Mobile Mode — Test mobile mode auto-zoom, force flag, pane switching, and status command\r\n  multi-window-registry: Multi-Window Registry — Test multi-window pane registry, review window isolation, and heal on restart\r\n  my-reg: My Reg\r\n  pane-layout: Pane Layout Refresh — Test that pane kill/relaunch properly refreshes layout\r\n  plans-pane: Plans Pane — Test plans view toggle, navigation, actions, and refresh persistence\r\n  pr-interaction: PR Interaction — Test PR navigation, selection, status changes, and actions\r\n  restart-dedup: TUI Restart Pane Deduplication — Test that restarting TUI doesn't create duplicate panes\r\n  session-resume: Cluster Session Resume — Test that cluster explore sessions are saved and resumed correctly\r\n  status-filter: Status Filter & Merged Toggle — Test F key status filter cycling and X key merged PR toggle\r\n  sync-refresh: Sync Re"]
[0.056204, "o", "fresh — Test r key sync, log line updates, and PR status changes\r\n  tech-tree-visual: Tech Tree Visual Review — Review tech tree appearance for visual issues and improvements\r\n  window-resize: Window Resize Rebalance — Test that layout auto-rebalances on window resize (portrait vs landscape)\r\n\r\nArtifact Recipes (3):\r\n  cli-recording: CLI Recording — Capture an asciinema replay of one or more CLI commands\r\n  my-art: My Art\r\n  tmux-screen-recording: tmux Screen Recording — Capture a tmux pane transcript and an asciinema replay\r\n\r\n"]
