[0.679962, "o", "Usage: pm tui [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...\r\n\r\n  Launch the interactive TUI (alias for ``pm session``).\r\n\r\n  Subcommands control and monitor a running TUI from the command line.\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n  -h, --help  Show this message and exit.\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  capture        Configure frame capture settings.\r\n  clear-frames   Clear captured frames for a session.\r\n  clear-history  Clear the TUI frame history for a session.\r\n  frames         View captured TUI frames.\r\n  history        View recent TUI frames from history.\r\n  keys           Show available TUI keybindings.\r\n  restart        Restart the TUI.\r\n  send           Send keys to the TUI.\r\n  view           View current TUI output.\r\n"]
